    Buttons:      offs    display chords with note offset-time      dur     show note durations      dyn     show note dynamics      ins     show instrument of notes      tr      transpose selected chords by the amount (in midics)              contained in the text box to its left    Boxes      stcnt   Sets the number of staffs for the editor      zoom    zooms attack times of chords"))))